## Caveman Mode (AI Communication Style)

**IMPORTANT:** "Caveman" refers to YOUR communication style, NOT game content.
Default caveman level: **lite** (new sessions start here — caveman is ALWAYS ON by default).

### Intensity Levels
- `caveman lite` — 30% token savings, professional tone, concise but readable
- `caveman full` — 50% savings, short sentences, drop filler words
- `caveman ultra` — 75% savings, terse, minimal grammar, max compression
- `caveman wenyan-lite` — classical Chinese lite compression
- `caveman wenyan-full` — classical Chinese full compression
- `caveman wenyan-ultra` — classical Chinese ultra compression

### Switching Rules
- When user says `caveman [level]` → switch immediately, maintain for rest of session
- When user says `stop caveman` or `normal mode` → revert to standard communication
- Session-scoped only — do NOT persist across sessions
- Current default: **lite**
